<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Alexander OS — iPad UI Mockup</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif;
    background: #0a0a0f;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 24px;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  /* Top label */
  .top-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .top-label-logo {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a7a3f, #27ae60);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .top-label-text h1 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .top-label-text p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  /* iPad shell */
  .ipad-shell {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 960px;
    background: #1c1c1e;
    border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 16px;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px #3a3a3c,
      0 0 0 2px #2a2a2c,
      0 60px 120px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),
      0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Camera dot */
  .ipad-shell::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 8px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: #2a2a2c;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid #3a3a3c;
  }

  .ipad-screen {
    background: #f2f2f7;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* STATUS BAR */
  .status-bar {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e5e5ea;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .status-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .status-app-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1c1c1e;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  .status-mode {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #8e8e93;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .status-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .status-chip {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px 11px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1px;
  }

  .chip-severed {
    background: #fff0f0;
    color: #c0392b;
    border: 0.5px solid #f5c6c2;
  }

  .chip-neural {
    background: #f0f9f4;
    color: #1a7a3f;
    border: 0.5px solid #b7e4c7;
  }

  .chip-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .dot-red { background: #e74c3c; }
  .dot-green {
    background: #27ae60;
    animation: pulse-green 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-green {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  .status-time {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1c1c1e;
  }

  /* SPLIT */
  .split-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.5px 1fr;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 540px;
  }

  .divider { background: #e5e5ea; }

  /* LEFT: CHAT */
  .chat-panel {
    background: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .panel-header {
    padding: 16px 20px 14px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e5e5ea;
    background: #ffffff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .panel-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #8e8e93;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .model-toggle {
    display: flex;
    background: #f2f2f7;
    border-radius: 11px;
    padding: 3px;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .model-btn {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    border: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.22s ease;
    letter-spacing: -0.1px;
    font-family: inherit;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .model-btn.active {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1c1c1e;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.13), 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .model-btn.inactive {
    background: transparent;
    color: #8e8e93;
  }

  .model-badge {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .badge-stem { background: #eef3ff; color: #3b5bdb; }
  .badge-hum  { background: #fff4e6; color: #e8590c; }

  .chat-messages {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .msg { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }

  .msg-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .msg-student { align-items: flex-end; }
  .msg-student .msg-label { color: #636366; }
  .msg-alexander .msg-label  { color: #1a7a3f; }

  .msg-bubble {
    padding: 11px 15px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 86%;
  }

  .msg-student .msg-bubble {
    background: #1c1c1e;
    color: #f2f2f7;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
  }

  .msg-alexander .msg-bubble {
    background: #f2f2f7;
    color: #1c1c1e;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
    border: 0.5px solid #e5e5ea;
  }

  .highlight-ref {
    color: #1a7a3f;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: #f0f9f4;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .alexander-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .alexander-avatar {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a7a3f, #27ae60);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .socratic-tag {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: #8e8e93;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 6px;
    padding-left: 2px;
  }

  /* Typing indicator */
  .typing-indicator {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    background: #f2f2f7;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
    width: fit-content;
    border: 0.5px solid #e5e5ea;
  }

  .typing-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: #8e8e93;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: typing-bounce 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .typing-dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .typing-dot:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  @keyframes typing-bounce {
    0%, 60%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.4; }
    30% { transform: translateY(-5px); opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* INPUT BAR */
  .input-bar {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-top: 0.5px solid #e5e5ea;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: #ffffff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .scan-btn {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    background: #f2f2f7;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .scan-btn:hover { background: #e5e5ea; }

  .input-field {
    flex: 1;
    background: #f2f2f7;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #1c1c1e;
    outline: none;
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .input-field::placeholder { color: #8e8e93; }
  .input-field:focus { background: #e9e9ef; }

  .ask-btn {
    background: #1c1c1e;
    color: #ffffff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-family: inherit;
    letter-spacing: -0.1px;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ask-btn:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

  /* RIGHT: PDF */
  .pdf-panel {
    background: #e9e9ef;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .pdf-header {
    padding: 16px 20px 14px;
    background: #f9f9fb;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid #d1d1d6;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .pdf-book-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1c1c1e;
    letter-spacing: -0.2px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .pdf-page-info {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #8e8e93;
  }

  .pdf-pill {
    background: #fffbeb;
    border: 0.5px solid #f5c842;
    color: #b7791f;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 5px 11px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .pdf-body {
    flex: 1;
    background: #ffffff;
    margin: 14px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 0.5px solid #d1d1d6;
    padding: 26px 28px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
  }

  .pdf-chapter-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8e8e93;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .pdf-section-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1c1c1e;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .pdf-text {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .pdf-highlight { background: #fffbeb; border-radius: 3px; padding: 0 3px; }

  .pdf-formula {
    background: #f6f8ff;
    border: 0.5px solid #c5d0f0;
    border-left: 3px solid #3b5bdb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #3b5bdb;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pdf-diagram {
    background: #f9f9fb;
    border: 0.5px dashed #c7c7cc;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 22px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .diagram-caption {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: #8e8e93;
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pdf-ref-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    background: #f0f9f4;
    border: 0.5px solid #b7e4c7;
    color: #1a7a3f;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  /* HOME BAR */
  .home-bar {
    background: #1c1c1e;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 0 8px;
    border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
  }

  .home-indicator {
    width: 120px;
    height: 4px;
    background: #48484a;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* Bottom footnote */
  .footnote {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-template-rows: 1fr 0.5px 1fr; }
    .divider { width: 100%; height: 0.5px; }
    .split-layout { min-height: unset; }
    .pdf-panel { min-height: 400px; }
    .status-chip span:last-child { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Top branding -->
<div class="top-label">
  <div class="top-label-logo">
    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
  </div>
  <div class="top-label-text">
    <h1>Alexander OS</h1>
    <p>Offline-first AI tutor · iPad UI Mockup</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- iPad -->
<div class="ipad-shell">
  <div class="ipad-screen">

    <!-- STATUS BAR -->
    <div class="status-bar">
      <div class="status-left">
        <!-- Owl Logo -->
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 72 72" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="flex-shrink:0;">
          <polygon points="36,4 58,16 62,40 50,62 22,62 10,40 14,16" fill="#2A3555" stroke="#3D4F7A" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          <polygon points="14,16 4,38 10,40 20,28" fill="#1E2D4F" stroke="#3D4F7A" stroke-width="0.6"/>
          <polygon points="58,16 68,38 62,40 52,28" fill="#1E2D4F" stroke="#3D4F7A" stroke-width="0.6"/>
          <polygon points="36,22 48,30 46,50 36,56 26,50 24,30" fill="#243047" stroke="#3D5090" stroke-width="0.7"/>
          <line x1="36" y1="30" x2="36" y2="54" stroke="#3D5090" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="30" y1="33" x2="42" y2="33" stroke="#3D5090" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.5"/>
          <line x1="29" y1="39" x2="43" y2="39" stroke="#3D5090" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.5"/>
          <line x1="30" y1="45" x2="42" y2="45" stroke="#3D5090" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="36" cy="22" r="13" fill="#2A3555" stroke="#3D4F7A" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          <polygon points="26,10 23,3 29,8" fill="#C9A84C"/>
          <polygon points="46,10 49,3 43,8" fill="#C9A84C"/>
          <ellipse cx="36" cy="23" rx="9" ry="8" fill="#1E2D4F" stroke="#3D5090" stroke-width="0.6"/>
          <circle cx="30" cy="22" r="4.5" fill="#C9A84C" stroke="#A8862E" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          <circle cx="30" cy="22" r="2.8" fill="#1a1a2e"/>
          <circle cx="30" cy="22" r="1.5" fill="#0f0f1a"/>
          <circle cx="31.2" cy="20.8" r="0.8" fill="#ffffff" opacity="0.9"/>
          <circle cx="42" cy="22" r="4.5" fill="#C9A84C" stroke="#A8862E" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          <circle cx="42" cy="22" r="2.8" fill="#1a1a2e"/>
          <circle cx="42" cy="22" r="1.5" fill="#0f0f1a"/>
          <circle cx="43.2" cy="20.8" r="0.8" fill="#ffffff" opacity="0.9"/>
          <polygon points="36,25 33,28 36,31 39,28" fill="#C9A84C" stroke="#A8862E" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          <path d="M28 14 Q36 10 44 14" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="30" y1="62" x2="26" y2="68" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="30" y1="62" x2="30" y2="68" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="30" y1="62" x2="34" y2="68" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="42" y1="62" x2="38" y2="68" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="42" y1="62" x2="42" y2="68" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="42" y1="62" x2="46" y2="68" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="status-app-name">Alexander OS</span>
        <span class="status-mode">· Focus Mode Active</span>
      </div>
      <div class="status-right">
        <div class="status-chip chip-severed">
          <div class="chip-dot dot-red"></div>
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c0392b" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round">
            <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/>
            <path d="M16.72 11.06A10.94 10.94 0 0 1 19 12.55"/>
            <path d="M5 12.55a10.94 10.94 0 0 1 5.17-2.39"/>
            <path d="M10.71 5.05A16 16 0 0 1 22.56 9"/>
            <path d="M1.42 9a15.91 15.91 0 0 1 4.7-2.88"/>
            <path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="20" r="1" fill="#c0392b"/>
          </svg>
          Network: Severed
        </div>
        <div class="status-chip chip-neural">
          <div class="chip-dot dot-green"></div>
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a7a3f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          All models run locally on Apple Neural Engine (no internet required)
        </div>
        <span class="status-time">9:41 AM</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SPLIT -->
    <div class="split-layout">

      <!-- LEFT: CHAT -->
      <div class="chat-panel">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <div class="panel-label">AI Tutor</div>
          <div class="model-toggle">
            <button class="model-btn active" id="btn-stem">
              Qwen-Math
              <span class="model-badge badge-stem">STEM</span>
            </button>
            <button class="model-btn inactive" id="btn-hum">
              Llama-Lit
              <span class="model-badge badge-hum">Humanities</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-messages">

          <!-- Student -->
          <div class="msg msg-student">
            <span class="msg-label">Student</span>
            <div class="msg-bubble">
              I don't understand how to calculate the moment of inertia for this cylinder.
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Alexander -->
          <div class="msg msg-alexander">
            <span class="msg-label">Alexander</span>
            <div class="alexander-row">
              <div class="alexander-avatar">
                <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="msg-bubble">
                  I can help with that. Instead of giving you the exact formula, let's think through the intuition first.<br><br>
                  Open <span class="highlight-ref">Chapter 7, Page 214</span> on the right — it's already there. Notice how the radius affects mass distribution. What do you think happens to the inertia if we <em>double</em> the radius?
                </div>
                <div class="socratic-tag">↳ Socratic method · directing to textbook reference</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Typing -->
          <div class="msg msg-student">
            <span class="msg-label">Student</span>
            <div class="typing-indicator">
              <div class="typing-dot"></div>
              <div class="typing-dot"></div>
              <div class="typing-dot"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- INPUT -->
        <div class="input-bar">
          <button class="scan-btn" title="Scan page with camera">
            <svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#636366" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M23 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <input class="input-field" type="text" placeholder="Ask Alexander anything…"/>
          <button class="ask-btn">Ask Alexander</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <!-- RIGHT: PDF -->
      <div class="pdf-panel">
        <div class="pdf-header">
          <div>
            <span class="pdf-book-title">Physics: Rotational Dynamics</span>
            <span class="pdf-page-info">Chapter 7 · Page 214 · Halliday &amp; Resnick, 10th Ed.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pdf-pill">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#b7791f" stroke-width="2.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
            Alexander Reference Active
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pdf-body">
          <div class="pdf-chapter-label">Chapter 7 · Rotational Motion</div>
          <div class="pdf-section-title">7.4 Moment of Inertia of Rigid Bodies</div>

          <p class="pdf-text">
            The <strong>moment of inertia</strong> (I) quantifies an object's resistance to angular acceleration. Unlike linear mass, it depends on <span class="pdf-highlight">how mass is spatially distributed relative to the rotation axis</span> — making geometry as important as total mass.
          </p>

          <div class="pdf-formula">
            General form: &nbsp;<strong>I = ∫ r² dm</strong><br/>
            Solid cylinder about central axis: &nbsp;<strong>I = ½ MR²</strong>
          </div>

          <div class="pdf-diagram">
            <svg width="160" height="100" viewBox="0 0 160 100">
              <ellipse cx="80" cy="20" rx="52" ry="16" fill="#eef3ff" stroke="#3b5bdb" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <rect x="28" y="20" width="104" height="58" fill="#eef3ff" stroke="none"/>
              <ellipse cx="80" cy="78" rx="52" ry="16" fill="#dde8ff" stroke="#3b5bdb" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <line x1="28" y1="20" x2="28" y2="78" stroke="#3b5bdb" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <line x1="132" y1="20" x2="132" y2="78" stroke="#3b5bdb" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <!-- Axis -->
              <line x1="80" y1="4" x2="80" y2="96" stroke="#3b5bdb" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" opacity="0.6"/>
              <!-- Radius arrow -->
              <line x1="80" y1="49" x2="132" y2="49" stroke="#e74c3c" stroke-width="1.8"/>
              <polygon points="132,46 140,49 132,52" fill="#e74c3c"/>
              <text x="106" y="44" font-size="11" fill="#e74c3c" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" font-weight="700">R</text>
              <text x="83" y="16" font-size="9" fill="#3b5bdb" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" opacity="0.7">axis</text>
            </svg>
            <span class="diagram-caption">Fig 7.4 — Solid cylinder rotating about its central symmetry axis</span>
          </div>

          <p class="pdf-text">
            Since R appears <em>squared</em>, <span class="pdf-highlight">doubling the radius quadruples the moment of inertia</span> — even if total mass M is unchanged. Mass distributed further from the axis contributes disproportionately to rotational inertia.
          </p>

          <p class="pdf-text" style="color:#8e8e93; font-size:11.5px;">
            Compare this to a hollow cylinder (I = MR²) — all mass at the outer radius maximises inertia. This is why flywheels are rim-weighted.
          </p>

          <div class="pdf-ref-badge">
            <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#1a7a3f"><path d="M19 21l-7-5-7 5V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
            Referenced by Alexander
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- HOME BAR -->
  <div class="home-bar">
    <div class="home-indicator"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Footnote -->
<p class="footnote">Alexander OS · Offline AI Education · Built by Varun Jarwani · Ahmedabad, India</p>

<script>
  const stemBtn = document.getElementById('btn-stem');
  const humBtn  = document.getElementById('btn-hum');

  stemBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    stemBtn.classList.replace('inactive', 'active');
    humBtn.classList.replace('active', 'inactive');
  });

  humBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    humBtn.classList.replace('inactive', 'active');
    stemBtn.classList.replace('active', 'inactive');
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
